w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/0b178f3a4ac39a9ce3db1957c326fded/48e3dab58a1c470e-fd/s100x200/cc51897fe1d2639bc1189b23d4667dc38408a020.gif 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/0b178f3a4ac39a9ce3db1957c326fded/48e3dab58a1c470e-fd/s250x400/18e4a844ef400ce03ea07786d154b898b64f4461.gif 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/0b178f3a4ac39a9ce3db1957c326fded/48e3dab58a1c470e-fd/s400x600/64932b565160c15064825869668ef15abf959269.gif 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/0b178f3a4ac39a9ce3db1957c326fded/48e3dab58a1c470e-fd/s500x750/7f62d7be1466313fc91737442bb93ed9f5ee683b.gif 438w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 438px) 100vw, 438px\"></figure></div><p>I hope you all have had a wonderful morning so far!</p><p>My muse has been a bit more active, but less about writing right now.  Today I already have two brand spanking new memes queued up and posting later.  I’ve added a new tag for these <a href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/goodtransgirl/tagged/alexandria%20meme\">#alexandria meme</a> which can be found <a href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/goodtransgirl/tagged/alexandria%20meme\">here</a>.  I guess this is just a new area to play in for your friendly neighborhood goth trans girl shitposter!</p><p>(I was just looking at my message from yesterday and realized I must have taken “Remember to be the feral trans shitposter you want to see in the world today!” to heart, even though I forgot I said it, lol.)</p><p>I hope you all have a wonderful day! 🖤🖤🖤</p>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"goodtransgirl"},"post":{"id":"810801162320232448"},"content_raw":"<p>Good morning, Alexandria friends!</p><p>Happy Hump day!</p><div class=\"npf_row\"><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"498\" data-orig-width=\"438\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/0b178f3a4ac39a9ce3db1957c326fded/48e3dab58a1c470e-fd/s640x960/2f74080490d4477545de49b9117fcdc3a1a40181.gif\" data-orig-height=\"498\" data-orig-width=\"438\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/0b178f3a4ac39a9ce3"}],"baseline_notes":2,"baseline_ts":1774705101.464}